metadata.name: Creative Talents Magazine - Issue 001 #1/10
metadata.description:
Issue 001 of the Creative Talents magazine includes some amazing NFT art and photography.  

Learn about the Creative Talents behind some super NFT projects. Enjoy reading information about the artists and the reasons behind the projects.

This NFT is a Cover variant showing artwork by James Hurley and you can access a pdf download of the magazine via: https://cldebmk670000jr08lzq5tc2d.orvylle.xyz/ once this token has been purchased and is in your wallet.

The Creative Talents Magazine is building a Community Interests Company which aims to help artists increase their Authority and Authenticity by publishing their artwork and Bios FREE of charge.
